data.description: LOCATION!!!!!!LOCATION !!!!!!!!!Amazing new construction home in a desirable and centralized area of Lehigh Acres, close to SR-82 and Daniels Pkwy. This beautiful home offers 3 Bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, white cabinets, tile floors, gorgeous granite countertops, stainless steel appliances with vaulted ceilings, two-car garage, a spacious screened lanai. The Master bedroom has two walk-in closets, dual sinks, a shower with glass enclosure, Additional pictures coming soon. The home will be completed by the end of May, 2023.
